Name: Installers Checklist (P-01 to P-12 & P-101 to P-112)
Temporary Fix ID Plate to Formwork
Use Aluminimum Formwork on Top Sides & Timber on Bottom Edge
Install Reo as-per Shop Drawing Plan
Lifters to be Firm & Square against Formwork
Finish Required - GOOD as near face is outside face of building
QA - Final Check of ALL measurerments & Photos
QA - Concrete Mix N40 Panel Mix
QA - Check Concrete mix % before accepting. Allow enough mix time.
NOT TO BE POURED WITHOUT APPROVAL FROM ENGINEER
